<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Exchange Index Up 3.37 Points </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, September 12 (Xinhua) -- The general price index at
Tehran Stock Exchange on Saturday closed at 1,516.64 points, up
3.37 points compared to the figure on Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
A total of 693,101 shares worth over 2.98 billion rials (about
542,000 U.S. dollars) changed hands in 688 turns for 361
applicants. The shares of 39 companies made gains while those of
12 others declined. 
