<HEADLINE> Mozambican President Willing to Mediate for Peace </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MAPUTO, September 12 (Xinhua) -- Mozambican Presi dent Joaquim
Chissano said here Saturday that he would like to mediate for
solution to the crisis in the Democratic Republic of Congo (DRC)
as long as he is invited.
</P>
