<HEADLINE> Albanian President Calls for Peace </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TIRANA, September 13 (Xinhua) -- The Albanian President Rexhep
Meidani Sunday called on all sides to keep sober-minded after the
assasination of opposition leader Azem Hajdari on Saturday night.
</P>
<P>
Meidani, who had immediately cut short his visit to Greece when
