<TEXT>
<P>
KUALA LUMPUR, September 13 (Xinhua) -- Following are the
results of swimming finals at the Commonwealth Games on Saturday
(race distances in meters):
</P>
<P>
Men
</P>
<P>
100 breaststroke
</P>
<P>
1. Simon Cowley, Australia, 1 minute, 2.00 seconds
