<HEADLINE> Tour of Spain Eighth Stage Results/Standings </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
1. Fabrizio Guidi, Italy, Polti, four hours 16 minutes 21
seconds
</P>
<P>
2. Peter van Petegem, Belgium, TVM
