<HEADLINE> Sony to Bid for Newcastle Club </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, September 12 (Xinhua) -- Japanese electronics giant
Sony Corp is bidding for English Premier League Club Newcastle
United at a price of 220 million pounds (371.3 million U.S.
dollars), according to the Saturday Mirror newspaper.
</P>
