talks with Newcastle's financial advisers, the paper said.
</P>
<P>
It quoted a Sony spokesman as saying: "We are considering
going into the football sector and Newcastle is one of the clubs
we are interested in."
</P>
<P>
Former Chelsea manager and Dutch international Gullit was
appointed manager of Newcastle just two weeks ago after Kenny
Dalglish was sacked.
</P>
<P>
Earlier on Saturday, Shearer scored twice as Newcastle beat
Southampton 4-0, their first league win of the season. 
